585
00:36:04,420 --> 00:36:05,820
would step up like me.

586
00:36:08,220 --> 00:36:09,060
My Lady,

587
00:36:09,620 --> 00:36:10,500
did they remind you

588
00:36:10,500 --> 00:36:11,660
of your own father?

589
00:36:14,860 --> 00:36:15,980
We don't have

590
00:36:15,980 --> 00:36:17,100
a family rule

591
00:36:17,100 --> 00:36:18,700
to defend the nation or hold no regrets.

592
00:36:19,780 --> 00:36:20,980
Father kept telling me

593
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:23,500
death was always a part of battle

594
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:25,500
and I should protect myself.

595
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:32,940
But everybody feels sympathy.

596
00:36:34,020 --> 00:36:35,420
When I just came here yesterday,

597
00:36:35,860 --> 00:36:36,780
I didn't understand.

598
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,020
But anyway,

599
00:36:39,020 --> 00:36:39,900
they moved me.

600
00:36:43,140 --> 00:36:44,220
In my opinion,

601
00:36:45,220 --> 00:36:46,460
people defend this nation

602
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:47,300
in different ways.

603
00:36:47,900 --> 00:36:48,740
But all in all,

604
00:36:49,380 --> 00:36:50,700
they share the same goal.

605
00:36:52,260 --> 00:36:53,100
Yeah.

606
00:36:54,580 --> 00:36:55,500
Some wanted to live

607
00:36:56,620 --> 00:36:58,220
but ended up dead.

608
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:02,340
There are always people
who sacrifice for justice.

609
00:37:02,900 --> 00:37:04,300
Those people are heroes.

610
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:06,580
Since I can't be one of them,

611
00:37:07,340 --> 00:37:08,740
I should protect them

612
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:09,980
from being insulted.

613
00:37:13,780 --> 00:37:14,660
What happened today

614
00:37:15,220 --> 00:37:16,100
hardened my resolve

615
00:37:16,580 --> 00:37:17,580
to find out the truth

616
00:37:17,580 --> 00:37:18,740
of the crossbow case.

617
00:37:21,060 --> 00:37:21,980
But once we manage

618
00:37:21,980 --> 00:37:23,260
to get General Wei Yun out,

619
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:24,780
won't it be harder

620
00:37:24,780 --> 00:37:25,820
to investigate that case?

621
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:27,060
Only after I get Wei Yun out

622
00:37:27,300 --> 00:37:28,260
can I feel more secure.

623
00:37:31,200 --> 00:37:32,080
The Arsenal Bureau

624
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:33,800
is an important military site.

625
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:36,160
If Wei Yun is convicted

626
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:37,320
and his family falls,

627
00:37:37,640 --> 00:37:39,320
the supervisor of the Arsenal Bureau

628
00:37:39,320 --> 00:37:40,640
will be someone else.

629
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:44,480
Then, it'll be harder to sneak in.

630
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:48,400
For whatever reason,

631
00:37:48,960 --> 00:37:50,320
I have to get Wei Yun out.

632
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:53,320
Then, My Lady,

633
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:55,440
have you come up with a plan?

634
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:06,960
(The Court of Judicial Review)

635
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:12,160
My Lord.

636
00:38:12,480 --> 00:38:14,320
My Lord.

637
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,320
Please let us out.

638
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:17,040
We're innocent.

639
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:18,000
My Lord.

640
00:38:18,840 --> 00:38:19,680
My Lord.

641
00:38:50,240 --> 00:38:51,200
It's stuffy in here.

642
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:53,680
In case you can hardly breathe,

643
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:55,480
I had you attended to first.

644
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:03,080
If looks could kill,

645
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,320
I'm afraid

646
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:06,160
you'd have killed me a thousand times.

647
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,080
But under such circumstances,

648
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,480
even if I let you down,

649
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:22,360
would you dare to kill me?

650
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,680
You never had any conflict with us.

651
00:39:31,560 --> 00:39:33,480
Someone must have ordered you,

652
00:39:34,720 --> 00:39:37,320
so you dared to exterminate us.

653
00:39:39,040 --> 00:39:40,080
We always handle a case

654
00:39:40,280 --> 00:39:41,640
under the order of authorities.

655
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:42,840
But this time,

656
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,800
it's His Majesty who gave an order.

657
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:49,440
I don't think it's His Majesty.

658
00:39:52,440 --> 00:39:53,280
It's...

659
00:39:56,200 --> 00:39:57,440
The Duke of Ning.

660
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:00,640
If my family falls,

661
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,640
the one who benefits the most

662
00:40:04,160 --> 00:40:06,320
will be the Duke of Ning,
head of the civil officials.

663
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:15,360
Cao Yan,

664
00:40:17,520 --> 00:40:19,800
His Majesty hates the clique thing most.

665
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:24,440
You're knowingly defying him.

666
00:40:28,080 --> 00:40:29,680
You're truly Wei Zhong's son.

667
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:31,120
Wei Yun,

668
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:33,760
you're really clever.

669
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:36,080
But sadly,

670
00:40:42,400 --> 00:40:44,400
even if you know the truth,

671
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,920
what can you do to me?

672
00:40:48,360 --> 00:40:49,520
You don't think

673
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,320
you can leave alive,

674
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:52,600
do you?

675
00:41:09,200 --> 00:41:10,040
Wei Yun,

676
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:12,120
your family got 70,000 soldiers killed.

677
00:41:12,680 --> 00:41:13,520
Do you or do you not

678
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,760
plead guilty?

679
00:41:17,720 --> 00:41:18,920
We are innocent.

680
00:41:22,920 --> 00:41:23,800
Not guilty!

681
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:27,600
Very well.

682
00:42:59,981 --> 00:43:03,431
♪If not for dreams by windswept flight♪

683
00:43:04,131 --> 00:43:07,281
♪How would my hand find yours tonight?♪

684
00:43:08,731 --> 00:43:12,151
♪This moonlit glow, in dusk's soft veil♪

685
00:43:12,531 --> 00:43:15,771
♪Hears heartbeats tell their secret tale♪

686
00:43:17,211 --> 00:43:20,961
♪Thoughts ablaze like beacon's fire♪

687
00:43:21,751 --> 00:43:25,201
♪Outline your form in golden lyre♪

688
00:43:26,061 --> 00:43:29,871
♪Through thorns we've trod and trials passed♪

689
00:43:30,281 --> 00:43:33,561
♪Each grief and joy forever cast♪

690
00:43:34,301 --> 00:43:37,641
♪Let the fierce warmth within your gaze♪

691
00:43:38,691 --> 00:43:42,251
♪Melt this war-torn world's cruel maze♪

692
00:43:42,981 --> 00:43:46,331
♪Still through the frost, I'll walk with you♪

693
00:43:46,641 --> 00:43:50,411
♪Our mountains and our streams anew♪

694
00:43:51,831 --> 00:43:53,971
♪Dawns greet the spring we longed to see♪

695
00:43:53,971 --> 00:43:55,921
♪Through meadows where wild larks soar free♪

696
00:43:56,091 --> 00:44:00,001
♪Let countless sails cross this worldly tide♪

697
00:44:00,521 --> 00:44:02,711
♪When lonely shadows turn to two♪

698
00:44:02,711 --> 00:44:06,531
♪Through countless turns and all we've borne♪

699
00:44:07,001 --> 00:44:09,031
♪No regret ever could be sworn♪

700
00:44:09,271 --> 00:44:11,501
♪Dawns greet the spring we longed to see♪

701
00:44:11,501 --> 00:44:13,491
♪Beneath heaven's vault, in harmony♪

702
00:44:13,681 --> 00:44:17,831
♪Let tears now fall for yesterday's strife♪

703
00:44:18,551 --> 00:44:24,391
♪We've reached this blossom-covered hill♪

704
00:44:25,561 --> 00:44:30,401
♪I'll follow you through every dream♪

